 lit between two organizations: Ele Elna Elak (a volunteer-driven initiativ
 e dedicated to supporting Palestinian families in need) and Chez Doris (a 
 Montreal-based organization that offers a safe\, non-discriminatory space 
 where women can receive support to regain their dignity and rebuild their 
 lives).\n&nbsp\;\nPart of Yell Out Fest 2026\nSaturday Punk Market + Works
 hops (Les Révoltes)\nFeminist Comedy Show (Casa del Popolo)\nSaturday Sho
 w (La Sotterenea)
